verses.verse: (Josh. 10:41; 11:16) Goshen, Holon, and Giloh: eleven cities with their villages;
Humtah, (Josh. 14:15) Kirjath Arba (which is Hebron), and Zior: nine cities with their villages;
Kain, Gibeah, and Timnah: ten cities with their villages;
Maarath, Beth Anoth, and Eltekon: six cities with their villages;
